# Eval case: freelance-invoice-gst

IDEA="Create a local invoicing tool for an Indian freelancer. Manage clients and projects, generate GST-compliant invoices with deterministic tax computation (CGST/SGST/IGST based on place of supply), track payment status, and produce a Markdown income summary per financial year. A local LLM drafts polite payment-reminder text from structured invoice fields only."

CONTEXT="Target: single freelancer, laptop-only, no cloud sync. Stack: Python CLI; SQLite (encrypted); Jinja2 invoice templates; Ollama 7B optional for reminder drafting. Formats: manual client/invoice entry; CSV export of invoices. Limits: max 50 active clients; INR only. Non-goals: GST return filing; payment-gateway integration; cloud LLM default; React UI; multi-user accounting; PDF rendering engine in v1; emailing invoices automatically. Defer: recurring invoices; multi-currency; expense tracking."
